{"tid":352633,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"林敏驄嗌欣宜肥婆","createTime":"2017-08-09T02:08:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T09:03:30.000Z","uid":49279,"like":798,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d2a70c47efb12e270762310a65085e01746b1155","tid":352633,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:08:22.000Z","msg":"張繼聰、林敏驄、林盛斌（Bob）、雨僑及連詩雅昨晚在尖沙嘴天星碼頭為電影《西謊極落：太爆．太子．太空艙》宣傳，林敏驄姍姍來遲，一班演員已在台上作自我介紹，Bob即刻指摘他說：<span style=\"color: red;\">「林敏驄搞錯呀！遲到！」</span>林敏驄上台後即爆肚，笑缺席的欣宜是肥婆，他說：「個肥婆呢？個肥婆冇嚟嘅！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張繼聰最近將兒子送到上海的車路士學校進行習訓，他說：「我阿爸有跟佢上去，當爺爺放暑假，佢初初都好唔慣，之後見到佢自己洗衫，都老懷安慰，個仔第一次同屋企分開咁耐時間，如果佢鍾意踢波，會支持佢做職業足球員。」"},{"pid":"5aab121b3439592f7354a1dbd611c332d76329e2","tid":352633,"uid":102132,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:10:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2bf20643327c56f2df81ecc51aabcc7741dad61","tid":352633,"uid":25794,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637b0876f948334d3168bb025fa04edf17f03f9d","tid":352633,"uid":3971,"like":10,"dislike":26,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:12:10.000Z","msg":"林把口幾衰"},{"pid":"07330601503a0b4edbe45820e9ec6bc205453223","tid":352633,"uid":17081,"like":439,"dislike":6,"score":433,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:34:10.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.giphy.com/l0HlLIgTarrJGUe5i.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.giphy.com%2Fl0HlLIgTarrJGUe5i.gif&h=7cb51ce7&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/photos31.flickr.com/38523366_c4f1279611_o.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fphotos31.flickr.com%2F38523366_c4f1279611_o.gif&h=3f594146&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"6a6f6cb1e2df7de4c2d5942e4006d